OL,3,CCalls to make 'life-changing' diabetes
OL,4,Ctreatment available in NI
OL,6,FThere have been calls for a pioneering
OL,7,Ftreatment that could transform life
OL,8,Ffor people with type 1 diabetes to be
OL,9,Fmade available in Northern Ireland.
OL,11,FTens of thousands of children and
OL,12,Fadults living across England are set
OL,13,Fto receive an "artificial pancreas",
OL,14,Fas part of a world-first initiative
OL,15,Fbeing rolled out by the NHS.
OL,17,FThe new device continually monitors a
OL,18,Fperson's blood glucose, then
OL,19,Fautomatically adjusts the amount of
OL,20,Finsulin given to them through a pump.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G1/8
