OL,3,CCalls to make 'life-changing' diabetes
OL,4,Ctreatment available in NI
OL,6,FThe Health Department has confirmed it
OL,7,Fis considering introducing the
OL,8,Ftreatment in Northern Ireland -
OL,9,Fcampaigners and patients here have
OL,10,Fwarned they can't be left behind.
OL,12,FAlan Hall, who lives with type 1
OL,13,Fdiabetes, said: "It would make you
OL,14,Ffeel, not that I don't feel normal,
OL,15,Fbut it would make you feel more normal
OL,16,Fin your day-to-day life.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G2/8
