OL,3,CCalls to make 'life-changing' diabetes
OL,4,Ctreatment available in NI
OL,6,F"Something like this ... it takes the
OL,7,Fmental load of the whole thing off
OL,8,Fbecause that's really what diabetes is
OL,9,Fmore about, it's more about all that
OL,10,Fthinking, about every minute of the
OL,11,Fday of trying to know what your sugar
OL,12,Flevel, is or what you're going to eat
OL,13,Fnext."
OL,15,FLocal NHS systems in England are now
OL,16,Fidentifying eligible people living
OL,17,Fwith type 1 diabetes who health chiefs
OL,18,Fbelieve could benefit from the Hybrid
OL,19,FClosed Loop system.
