OL,3,CCalls to make 'life-changing' diabetes
OL,4,Ctreatment available in NI
OL,6,FThe technology will mean some people
OL,7,Fwith type 1 diabetes will no longer
OL,8,Fneed to inject themselves with insulin
OL,9,Fbut rely on technology to receive
OL,10,Fmedication.
OL,12,FIt is said to also help prevent life-
OL,13,Fthreatening hypoglycaemic and
OL,14,Fhyperglycaemia attacks, which can lead
OL,15,Fto seizures, coma, or even death for
OL,16,Fpeople living with type 1 diabetes.
OL,18,FThousands of people are living with
OL,19,Ftype 1 diabetes in Northern Ireland.
