OL,4,Ctreatment available in NI
OL,6,FRoxanne Small from Diabetes UK
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland said: "We use the
OL,8,Fwords groundbreaking, life-changing,
OL,9,Fbut we don't use that easily - it's
OL,10,Freally going to be such a significant
OL,11,Fchange.
OL,13,F"For people who have lived with type 1
OL,14,Ffor a long time, they're telling us
OL,15,Fthey can't begin to imagine what
OL,16,Fthat's going to feel like to have
OL,17,Ftechnology like the hybrid closed loop.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G5/8
