OL,6,F"It's going to create a world where
OL,7,Fyes, diabetes is still part of it, but
OL,8,Fit shouldn't be as life-limiting in
OL,9,Fthe things you want to do any more."
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the Health
OL,12,FDepartment said: "The National
OL,13,FInstitute for Health and Care
OL,14,FExcellence (NICE) published final
OL,15,Fguidance on Hybrid closed loop systems
OL,16,Ffor managing blood glucose levels in
OL,17,Ftype 1 diabetes in December 2023.
