OL,6,F"This was subsequently endorsed by the
OL,7,FDepartment of Health and work is now
OL,8,Fongoing to consider commissioning and
OL,9,Fimplementation arrangements in
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,12,F"Significant additional investment
OL,13,Fwill be required to support the
OL,14,Fprovision of Hybrid Closed Loop
OL,15,Fsystems to people living with Type 1
OL,16,Fdiabetes who would be eligible.
